{"tid":1851584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人民日報--維護國家主權比起人民健康重要","createTime":"2020-01-30T05:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T06:08:18.000Z","uid":17641,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"230988f9be2d959b76899d6596d601422df3376e","tid":1851584,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e2bc7e5ffe2e0495e9073d8657e87e72e1e07f","tid":1851584,"uid":315387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"老Zac認同"},{"pid":"30a7f89621ddb45e0462e231bf860439a0e0301d","tid":1851584,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：種族清洗 香港人，仲唔反佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851323</a>"},{"pid":"62e2d58ab611d8895781308e95b861ef97f87dc3","tid":1851584,"uid":46213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://businessfocus.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/plane155-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=830\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2Fplane155-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A